# CODEOWNERS — Kokkeak_API
#
# Maps path → reviewer handle. GitHub auto-assigns reviewers when a
# PR touches a matching path. The "fallback" rule at the bottom
# catches everything else so no file slips through review.
#
# Conventions:
#   - First match wins (GitHub reads top-down).
#   - Owners receive review requests; team handles still optional.
#   - Keep this file in lockstep with `crates/*` ownership.
#
# Update alongside CONTRIBUTING.md when teams change.

# Default owner: core API team owns everything until a more
# specific rule below matches. Acts as a safety net so PRs
# without a closer match still get a review request.
*                                       @kokkak/backend-core

# ----- Domain & application logic -----
# Business rules, entities, use cases. Touching these usually
# means a domain change — needs senior review.
/crates/domain/                         @kokkak/backend-domain
/crates/application/                    @kokkak/backend-domain

# ----- Persistence & adapters -----
# SQL / Mongo / Redis / NATS / S3 / FCM wiring. Schema changes
# live here too; coordinate with DBA.
/crates/infra/                          @kokkak/backend-infra
/migrations/                            @kokkak/backend-infra

# ----- HTTP surface -----
# Routes, handlers, middleware, OpenAPI spec, TLS config.
/crates/api/                            @kokkak/backend-api
/crates/api/src/openapi.rs              @kokkak/backend-api

# ----- Async workers -----
# NATS consumer / producer handlers. Coordinate with infra for
# queue subject conventions.
/crates/worker/                         @kokkak/backend-workers

# ----- Shared cross-cutting concerns -----
# Errors, config, telemetry, i18n. Any crate can import these,
# so they need a broad review.
/crates/common/                         @kokkak/backend-core

# ----- Deploy & release -----
# Anything that ships to prod: Dockerfile, compose, helm, CI/CD.
Dockerfile                              @kokkak/platform
.dockerignore                           @kokkak/platform
/docker-compose.yml                     @kokkak/platform
/deploy/                                @kokkak/platform
/.github/workflows/                     @kokkak/platform

# ----- Project-wide docs that affect everyone -----
/CONTRIBUTING.md                        @kokkak/backend-core
/AGENTS.md                              @kokkak/backend-core
